<!doctype html>
<html lang="de">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Nominatim</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: light;
        --bg: #f4f0e8;
        --panel: #fffdf8;
        --ink: #1f2a2e;
        --muted: #5d6a6f;
        --accent: #1d6f5f;
        --accent-2: #d8efe8;
        --border: #d8d1c5;
      }
      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
        color: var(--ink);
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top left, #ffffff 0, #f4f0e8 42%),
          linear-gradient(180deg, #efe7da 0%, var(--bg) 100%);
      }
      main {
        max-width: 880px;
        margin: 4rem auto;
        padding: 0 1.25rem;
      }
      .panel {
        background: var(--panel);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 18px;
        padding: 2rem;
        box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(31, 42, 46, 0.08);
      }
      h1 {
        margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.4rem);
        line-height: 0.95;
      }
      p {
        margin: 0 0 1rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 1.05rem;
      }
      form {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
        gap: 0.75rem;
        margin: 1.5rem 0 1rem;
      }
      input {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 0.9rem 1rem;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 12px;
        font: inherit;
      }
      button {
        border: 0;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 0.9rem 1.2rem;
        background: var(--accent);
        color: white;
        font: inherit;
        cursor: pointer;
      }
      .links {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 0.75rem;
        margin-top: 1.25rem;
      }
      a {
        color: var(--accent);
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .link-card {
        background: var(--accent-2);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
      }
      code {
        font-family: "SFMono-Regular", Consolas, monospace;
        font-size: 0.95em;
      }
      @media (max-width: 700px) {
        form { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <section class="panel">
        <h1>Nominatim</h1>
        <p>Lokale Geocoding-Instanz fuer Schleswig-Holstein.</p>
        <p>Die API laeuft bereits. Ueber die Suche unten kannst du direkt einen Nominatim-Request gegen <code>/search</code> ausloesen.</p>

        <form action="/search" method="get">
          <input type="text" name="q" placeholder="Flensburg, Schleswig oder eine Adresse" required>
          <input type="hidden" name="format" value="jsonv2">
          <button type="submit">Suchen</button>
        </form>

        <div class="links">
          <a class="link-card" href="/status">Status</a>
          <a class="link-card" href="/search?q=Flensburg&amp;format=jsonv2">Beispielsuche</a>
          <a class="link-card" href="/reverse?lat=54.7833&amp;lon=9.4333&amp;format=jsonv2">Reverse Beispiel</a>
          <a class="link-card" href="/lookup?format=jsonv2">Lookup</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
